{"tid":120030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7警裁決】高志森fb辱罵法官「狗官」 吸藍絲留言跟住鬧","createTime":"2017-02-14T07:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T09:48:01.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a52730a5b24b1230bcc7c36a8fd0521bd385a8","tid":120030,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170214/large/1487056256_a37f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F1487056256_a37f.jpg&h=55e3c63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7警案今日終有裁決，裁定各被告有意圖而導致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪名不成立，但交替的襲擊致他人受傷控罪則全部罪成，另外第五被告另被裁定普通襲擊罪成，各人須還柙。導演高志森疑不滿裁決，在facebook辱罵法官，斥「黃絲法官偏幫亂港反港份子」，甚至形容法官為「狗官」，指「本土港獨暴徒縱火、打警察、破壞公物，狗官就輕判、甚至判無罪，實在偏頗至極」。<br />\n<br />\n其侮辱言論竟有大批藍絲留言力撐，有人形容「黑暗司法」，反問警察如何再執法，又指裁決「無天理」。"},{"pid":"0cc3a71ba2b6c2b8ae72cd3cc7bea14661541dbf","tid":120030,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"算唔算藐視法庭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654624b185e1c0760f68c9c674db88b3ffede987","tid":120030,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"算唔算誹謗 同埋 不誠實使用電腦"},{"pid":"92454ef256453708f170fe7f79b22690e30670bc","tid":120030,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"有冇得告藐視法庭??"},{"pid":"1d2def850573a1da2517b155aed93e940b6ee83e","tid":120030,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5739e21f73e83b7c2a401a105374ee39074a2918","tid":120030,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/